ed.

I mean =E2=80=A6=C2=A0they=E2=80=99ll =E2=80=A6=C2=A0buy them back =E2=80=
=A6=C2=A0at $1? Like that=E2=80=99s the point? Of Tether? What are we doing=
 here? Like if you see a stock go from $10 to $100 and think =E2=80=9Chahah=
a this is a great short=E2=80=9D and short it at $100, one thing that might=
