<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
ess.com/click/28231054.277586/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL=
2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDYtMjgvZG9uLXQtY2hlYXQtb24tdGhlLWV0aGljcy1leGFtP2NtcGlk=
PUJCRDA2MzAyMl9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV=
0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIyMDYzMCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b852=
